rComments: Super nice guy.... not a good prof. His exams are insanely hard and have things we have never seen in class. He is a very hard grader and only 4 people out of a class of 38 got an 80 or above. His exams are insanely long even after him saying he would adjust the length, he did not. Only 2 50% exams. I would take any other prof.
AMAZING PROF!! But hard to get a good grade. One of my favorite prof!

Great prof, really nice guy and knows everything about physiology. Very interesting class and he is very good at explaining, although the midterm and final are worth 50% and its imposible to do good on them. They are not easy and its really hard to finish with a good grade in this course but overall really good prof
